  "detailed_description": "Are you ready for the next level of Tower Defense games?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Epic multiplayer battles</h2>Whether it's 1-on-1 or team-on-team: in the fast-paced multiplayer duels, every decision counts! While you're constantly sending monster troops to your opponent, you can't neglect your own defense. With each level up you can choose from dozens of skills to best support your playing style.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/cefc6d30a5e9e2ae1d1c05e1e536a6ab.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/d40e9535fc9aa916e7b34347fcc25ec2.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/24578d2780a13a5790deb384a24e1b39.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/62800a13a94d89f90f849c096ad4ec02.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/ab243293cc0baa9afad1289f8d850080.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/3d7b6144ccc0f59b64e4bb4cdbf1408c.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917850/extras/f55c3e32aaeedf3b6c23578355f3ced8.webp?t=1761559666\" width=50 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless sing